      "content": "i know u said to see a doctor but i cant get an appointment until monday morning and i literally can't function like this. i checked online and it said cipro is just a regular antibiotic used for infections. since it was prescribed to me before, how bad can it really be if i just take one or two to get through the night? it's just one dose, it's not like i'm starting a whole course or anything.",
